Package: scNoiseFilter
Type: Package
Title: Noise Gene Filtering for Single-Cell RNA-Seq Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Zhijun", "Feng", ,
    email = "fenzhj18@sina.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1813-1669"))
Description: A comprehensive tool for filtering noise genes in single-cell
    RNA-seq analysis. Supports mouse, rat, and human species. Identifies
    and filters Riken genes, predicted genes (Gm/RGD), 5-digit genes,
    ribosomal genes, mitochondrial genes, hemoglobin genes, and high-abundance
    background genes.
